    "content": "    This is the main riff, it is played through the whole song: just repeat it.\r\n\r\n[tab]G |: ----------------|\r\nD |: ----------------|\r\nA |: 3-------6---1---|\r\nE |: ----4-----------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n    Or you can play it like this:\r\n\r\n[tab]G |: ----------------|\r\nD |: ----------------|\r\nA |: 3-------6---5---|\r\nE |: ----4-----------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n    And really that's it. Please tell me if it needs to be corrected.",
